You're doing great. Lani. okay?
Breathe for me.

729
00:45:21.039 --> 00:45:22.479
You gotta breathe.
Give me your eyes.

730
00:45:22.519 --> 00:45:25.719
Breathe deep in. okay?
In. Out.

731
00:45:25.800 --> 00:45:27.800
Hey. Doctor's here.

732
00:45:27.880 --> 00:45:29.719
Oh. thank God.

733
00:45:29.800 --> 00:45:32.159
- Hey. Lani. I'm Dr. Rezz.
- Thank you.

734
00:45:32.239 --> 00:45:33.776
- We're here to take care of you.
- Thank you. thank you.

735
00:45:33.800 --> 00:45:35.615
Let me get some gloves.
check your vitals real quick.

736
00:45:35.639 --> 00:45:38.800
- It hurts so bad.
- How far apart are your contractions?

737
00:45:38.880 --> 00:45:41.039
- Two minutes.
- Two minutes?

738
00:45:41.119 --> 00:45:43.199
I just thought she was chunky.

739
00:45:43.280 --> 00:45:45.199
You know. the poor woman
was having a baby

740
00:45:45.280 --> 00:45:48.599
and I... I didn't even notice.

741
00:45:53.760 --> 00:45:55.000
Fuck.

742
00:46:45.760 --> 00:46:49.840
- Did you think that guy was hot?
- What guy?

743
00:46:49.920 --> 00:46:53.199
That guy you were gawking at
by the tiki torches.

744
00:46:56.719 --> 00:47:00.320
I don't remember seeing a guy
by the tiki torches.

745
00:47:05.440 --> 00:47:08.639
Quinn. what are you doing in there?
Are you fapping?

746
00:47:08.719 --> 00:47:10.119
Fuck off!

747
00:47:20.199 --> 00:47:22.760
Shit. Nicole. it's the doctor.

748
00:47:22.840 --> 00:47:25.559
I told you. today is tomorrow.
Answer it.

749
00:47:27.079 --> 00:47:28.760
Hello.

750
00:47:28.840 --> 00:47:31.480
- Mark Mossbacher?
- This is he.

751
00:47:31.559 --> 00:47:33.920
Hi. do you have
a minute for the doctor?

752
00:47:34.000 --> 00:47:35.440
Yeah. Of course.

753
00:47:35.519 --> 00:47:37.960
Okay. One second.
I'll put him right on.

754
00:47:38.039 --> 00:47:40.199
He's calling me first thing.

755
00:47:41.159 --> 00:47:42.559
Don't read into it.

756
00:48:00.320 --> 00:48:03.360
- I'm so sorry. Mark. I just lost him.
- What?

757
00:48:03.440 --> 00:48:05.679
Can we call you back
in a few minutes?

758
00:48:05.760 --> 00:48:08.320
Hey. I'm on vacation.
It's very late here.

759
00:48:08.400 --> 00:48:10.800
Can you just please get him back?

760
00:48:10.880 --> 00:48:12.920
I'm so sorry.
It'll just be a few minutes.

761
00:48:13.000 --> 00:48:15.840
I promise. Call you right back.

762
00:48:15.920 --> 00:48:18.280
- Okay.
- Okay. Thanks.

763
00:48:23.760 --> 00:48:25.440
It's gonna be okay. Mark.

764
00:48:28.280 --> 00:48:30.519
It's... it's gonna be good news.

765
00:48:30.599 --> 00:48:32.559
Good things happen to good people.

766
00:48:48.639 --> 00:48:50.400
We're married.

767
00:48:51.280 --> 00:48:53.079
We're on our honeymoon.

768
00:48:53.159 --> 00:48:56.039
Yeah. Yep.

769
00:48:58.400 --> 00:48:59.639
I'm happy.

770
00:49:01.239 --> 00:49:02.880
Yeah. Me. too.

771
00:49:02.960 --> 00:49:04.360
I just hope that we don't become

772
00:49:04.440 --> 00:49:07.119
like one of those
old. depressing couples

773
00:49:07.199 --> 00:49:11.960
with all this baggage
and resentment and regrets.

774
00:49:12.039 --> 00:49:14.199
And...

775
00:49:14.280 --> 00:49:17.679
I just hope it always stays
this way. you know?

776
00:49:17.760 --> 00:49:19.880
Yeah. It will. baba.

777
00:49:21.320 --> 00:49:23.679
- Promise?
- Yeah.

778
00:49:26.079 --> 00:49:27.559
Come here.

779
00:49:38.679 --> 00:49:40.719
We are always gonna feel like this.

780
00:49:41.400 --> 00:49:44.360
We will always be young.

781
00:49:44.440 --> 00:49:48.159
And we will always be in love.

782
00:49:48.239 --> 00:49:51.880
And there will be days
and days just like this.

783
00:49:55.239 --> 00:49:57.360
- Okay?
- Okay.
